{"tid":1660024,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"被捕後我仲可以做乜","createTime":"2019-10-17T09:16:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T18:06:50.000Z","uid":106574,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"1aecf7e24af0daaa802b2d6f588634c33334ead7","tid":1660024,"uid":106574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T09:16:04.000Z","msg":"我係10月13號被捕既其中一個人<br />\n而家已經出返黎<br />\n其實唔知自己呢刻可以仲可以做乜<br />\n又唔知會唔會比人監視住<br />\n又驚出返去會害埋其他人<br />\n又唔敢大肆share文宣圖<br />\n其實呢刻我唔知自己做咩係安全<br />\n因為我覺得自己單case唔係好嚴重<br />\n又唔想阻住律師<br />\n所以都無搵佢問啲咩<br />\n其實被捕我唔驚<br />\n但我覺得而家人越黎越少<br />\n大家仲有好多包伏放唔低<br />\n我真係好唔甘心場運動就咁就完左<br />\n每日睇到咁多難過既事發生<br />\n但呢刻我已經被停賽<br />\n到底我仲可以做乜野<br />\n最後好想大家記得唔好放棄<br />\n1020需要你地<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84080b12ef7eef0d7cb622e312f6ac125c674025","tid":1660024,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T09:16:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dC4rszp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"http